多谢，如果dataset是这种结构
```
option = {
    legend: {},
    tooltip: {},
    dataset: {
        dimension:['name','value'],
        source: [
            {name:'10', value:52.2},
            {name:'20', value:52.2},
            {name:'30', value:52.2},
            {name:'40', value:52.2},
            {name:'50', value:52.2}
        ]
    },
    xAxis: {type: 'category'},
    yAxis: {},
    series: [
        {type: 'pie'}
    ]
};
```
